      "content": "i hear you about the love part, i really do, but love doesn't pay the mortgage or fix the fact that they're all stressed because of me. it's just a loop. the more i try to \"be there\" for them, the more i feel like i'm just consuming their lives. sometimes it feels like the most loving thing i could actually do is just... remove the source of the stress. stop being a problem they have to solve every single day.",
